    <!-- UVT withholding tax table is implemented in Python code
         (co_payslip.py _compute_uvt_tax method) following Art. 383
         of the Colombian Tax Code (Estatuto Tributario).

         This file is a placeholder for reference.
         The table ranges are:
         0 - 95 UVT: 0%
         95 - 150 UVT: 19% marginal
         150 - 360 UVT: 28% marginal
         360 - 640 UVT: 33% marginal
         640 - 945 UVT: 35% marginal
         945 - 2300 UVT: 37% marginal
         2300+ UVT: 39% marginal
    -->
</odoo>
